messages.message: Hey team -- I think we are falling behind on this. None of the apps are updated on prod yet, and this will block prod push on Monday. @andy we need to prioritize this Monday morning PST. @Shubham, do you have all the new version of public apps ready to go? Can you share where the apps are?

Hi @Kerry, here is the spreadsheet (https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1aecwIY37wMuj9Zm3MfSZqXskGqFo6L1k/edit#gid=1678344335)  which has the ibsolution path (along with the publish type) for each of the application. Let us know if you need anything more than this.
